text: MLS Cup 2016 was a soccer game played on December 10, 2016. It was the 21st MLS Cup, a special game between the winners of the Eastern and Western Conferences in Major League Soccer. Seattle Sounders FC won the game in a penalty shootout with a score of 5–4 against Toronto FC.. The two teams played again in MLS Cup 2017. Toronto FC won that game 2–0. ==Sources== Category:Soccer in the United States Category:2016 in the United States
title: MLS Cup 2016
